    <p>For the more advanced users found on VPS and dedicated servers, command line scripts are available! Save time by working within the command line to quickly configure, investigate server issues, and execute commands.</p>

    <p>Some scripts included:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><em>cpbackup</em> - perform system wide backups</li>
